201
00:16:25,277 --> 00:16:29,197
Chicago has given us some
specific budgetary targets

202
00:16:29,281 --> 00:16:33,827
that will require some hard choices
throughout the newsroom.

203
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:36,538
We are, quite simply,

204
00:16:36,621 --> 00:16:39,958
going to have to find ways
to do more with less.

205
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:43,670
So I guess I will turn this over to Tom,

206
00:16:43,753 --> 00:16:46,173
