207
00:16:48,425 --> 00:16:49,777
I know some of you have questions.

208
00:16:49,801 --> 00:16:52,762
If you could hold them for me
until after I've had a chance to speak.

209
00:16:53,054 --> 00:16:55,765
Pull your clip book together.
Time to find a new home.

210
00:16:55,849 --> 00:16:57,493
Chicago has sent us a memo
outlining options

211
00:16:57,517 --> 00:16:58,997
that are available to those of you...

212
00:16:59,060 --> 00:17:01,771
The aorta should have elasticity to it,

213
00:17:01,855 --> 00:17:03,523
but it's rock-hard.

214
00:17:03,607 --> 00:17:06,902
Whoever strangled him
could've just waited a month or two more.

215
00:17:07,194 --> 00:17:09,196
This guy was on his last legs.

216
00:17:09,279 --> 00:17:10,906
It is what it is.

217
00:17:10,989 --> 00:17:13,158
In addition to the fractured hyoid
and the bruising,

218
00:17:13,241 --> 00:17:15,243
I got signs of a struggle around the body,

219
00:17:15,327 --> 00:17:20,415
